div.div:
pyrobenchorchestrates the process
it simulates requests topyroscope(push-mode)
it responds to requests frompyroscope(pull-mode)
at the end of a run it generates a report
pyroscope_mainis another instance of pyroscope server, but it's running the latest version from the main branch, and is intended to provide a baseline, something to compare your new version to

pyroscopeis the version that's currently being tested
it builds from local source code, allowing you to rapidly test variations of pyroscope
we provision a grafana instance so that you can see metrics live as they're coming frompyroscopeandpyroscope_main

rendereris used to generate screenshots of grafana dashboards
they later get posted
